Scripts to take an Ubuntu Touch image and remaster it for Kubuntu

remaster-ubuntu-touch - download ubuntu touch, upload it to the arm server, download remastered image from arm server

chroot-remaster - run in the chroot on the server to remaster the image

works with system-image from
http://bazaar.launchpad.net/~ubuntu-system-image/ubuntu-system-image/server/
